'Yan Majalisar Wakilai na Wales sun damu da cewa za a yi wasa da su
Wasu 'yan majalisar Welsh sun yi mamakin shawarar da aka dauka na maye gurbin mukamin su da MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga shirin sauya sunan majalisar, wanda zai zama majalisar dokokin Wales.
A fagen siyasa, wasu 'yan majalisar sun ce wannan zai iya zama abin ba'a.
Wani dan majalisar na Labour ya nuna damuwarsa cewa  ya yi kama da Twp da Pwp .
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa, kuma pwp yana nufin tururuwa.
A cewar wani daga cikin mambobinta, jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru (Jam'iyyar Wales) ba ta gamsu ba kuma ta ba da wasu shawarwari.
Jam'iyyar Conservative za ta kasance a shirye don canza sunan, amma ta lura cewa MWP da Muppet sun kasance a cikin ƙananan nisa.
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Welsh, ana kiran harafin w kamar yadda ake kiran harafin u a yaren Yorkshire na Turanci.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda a yanzu haka yake shirin yin dokar da za ta sauya sunan, ya ce, 'yan majalisar ne za su yanke shawara a kan sunayen 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa majalisar dokokin Wales ikon sauya sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta fitar da sakamakon shawarwarin jama'a kan batun sanya Majalisar a matsayin majalisar Welsh, wanda ya samu goyon baya sosai.
A kan batun taken membobin, Hukumar ta goyi bayan 'Yan Majalisar Welsh (ko WMP) duk da haka; yawancin Welsh sun fi son MWP.
Ana ganin 'yan majalisar na da wasu shawarwari, amma kokarin cimma yarjejeniya zai iya zama abin takaici ga Elin Jones, shugaban majalisar, wanda za a gabatar da dokar sauya sunan a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar sake fasalin za ta hada da wasu gyare-gyare kan yadda majalisa ke aiki, musamman dokokin da ke hana fitar da 'yan majalisa da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
'Yan majalisar za su yanke hukunci na karshe kan batun sunan yayin da suke tattaunawa kan kudirin dokar.
