Indonesia: Mutane 832 sun mutu a tsunami
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta ruwaito safiyar ranar Lahadi cewa, yawan mutanen da suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami ya kai 832.
Mutane da yawa sun makale a karkashin gine-gine da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta rushe a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da raƙuman ruwa mai tsawon mita 6, in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a wani taron manema labarai.
