Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa a fannin ilimin kere-kere
Yayin da China ke kara samun ci gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don bincike a fannin, a cewar Kai-Fu Lee, wani masanin ilimin kere kere da ya yi aiki a Google da Microsoft da kuma Apple.
Wannan ya biyo bayan sanarwar da wasu hukumomin gwamnatin Amurka suka yi game da AI, yayin da Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI.
A daidai wannan lokaci, kasar Sin ta gabatar da taswirar tafiyar da take yi a shekarar da ta gabata, inda ta ce tana son ta zama jagora a fannin kirkirar AI nan da shekara ta 2030.
"Kyau biyu na kudaden da ake bayarwa don binciken AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran kasashe sun fi Amurka gaba, kuma muna neman babbar nasara ta gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
Biyu na kudaden zai iya ninka damar da za a samu babban ci gaba a fannin AI daga Amurka, Lee ya fadawa CNBC a wata hira a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa  AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order  wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a cikin daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin 1980s, a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke dan wasan Amurka mafi girma na Othello. Daga baya ya shiga cikin ƙungiyar gudanarwa na Microsoft Reasearch kuma ya zama shugaban reshen Google na China.
Lee ya shiga gasar fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ta shirya, kamar gasar Robotics Challenge ta Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, kuma ya tambaya yaushe za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba, don gano masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka suna aiki tuƙuru don su samu kuɗi daga gwamnati.
 Kasar Sin ba ta kwace shugabanni na jami'o'i ba, kamfanoni ne , in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da wasu kamfanonin fasaha sun yi hayar manyan malamai don su yi aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya kara da cewa sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya tallafawa kokarin Amurka na AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba masu binciken AI katunan aiki kai tsaye", in ji shi.
Majalisar Harkokin Kasar Sin ta bayyana shirinta na bunkasa sabuwar fasahar kere kere ta zamani a watan Yulin 2017.
Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin ta ba da tallafi ga ma'aikatan cibiyoyin ilimi, kamar yadda Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da tallafi ga masu bincike na Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a China ya fi ƙasa, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hadin Kan Artificial Intelligence, wanda ya kamata ya haɗa da abokan hulɗa na masana'antu da na ilimi.Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓin Kan Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan ne DARPA ta sanar da cewa za ta zuba dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
NSF, a halin yanzu, tana ba da fiye da dala miliyan 100 a shekara don bincike a AI.
A gefe guda, dokar Amurka da ke neman kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa kan ilimin kere kere ba ta dauki mataki ba a cikin watanni da suka gabata.
