Amma ba mu san yawan lokacin da zai yi wasa ba.
"Kafin wata daya, kasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto a Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai iya buga wasa na 'yan mintuna kaɗan.
Bayan wasan motsa jiki, a farkon makon, an tambayi James game da shirye-shiryensa na kakar wasa ta bana, wanda ya hada da wasanni shida.
 A wannan lokaci na sana'ata, ba na bukatar wasannin farko na kakar wasa don in kasance a shirye. 
Yaƙin neman zaɓe na Trump a West Virginia (Hanyar YouTube)
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara jerin tarukan yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
An kuma shirya za a sake yin amfani da jirgin a wasu jihohi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi inda shugaban ƙasar yake da farin jini.
Da aka dage kada kuri'ar tabbatar da matsayin Kotun Koli, Trump na neman ya tara goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar wa'adi mai zuwa kuma ya hana 'yan Republican rasa ikon majalisar a zaben na Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana a daren yau kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, don karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya bin diddigin sa a yanar gizo a kasa, kai tsaye a YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai tattauna batun sauraron karar da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli na Amurka Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zarge shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, a wannan makon, kuma ana sa ran za a dage zaben tabbatar da Kavanaugh a majalisar dattawa har zuwa mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken da FBI ke yi.
Amma wannan taron na da muhimmanci ne domin taimakawa 'yan Republican su samu nasara a zaben Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, shugaban na Amurka ya bayyana a cikin yakin neman zabensa cewa, taron na da nufin karfafa gwiwar masu sa kai da magoya bayan jam'iyyar a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai.
"Sarrafa Majalisa wani muhimmin bangare ne na shirin shugaban wanda zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a lokacin da ya fara yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ba.
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, taron na daren yau, wanda aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, zai iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma ya jawo hankalin 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, za ta zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda zuwa West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe a 2016 da fiye da maki 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar Sanata na Jamhuriyar West Virginia, wanda ke bin baya a kuri'un neman zabe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya sake tayar da shi a cikin zaɓe", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Ƙungiyar Amurka a shirye take ta yi gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan da za ta yi a gasar zakarun Turai ta ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasan farko da na uku, wasan da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma ya zama daidai abin da Ryder Cup ya rasa.
Yin wasan balancer na zuma ra'ayin wasa ne da aka ƙera shi da kansa amma 'yan wasan suna gaskata da shi da gaske, kuma sun fi yin hakan a gasa kamar wannan.
To, a ina ne za su iya samun Isalan a yanzu?
"Sun riga sun kai mu da maki shida, yanzu sun kai mu da maki hudu, don haka wannan ya ba mu wata dama", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da ya ke komawa wasannin yau.
A'a, Turai ce ke kan gaba da maki huɗu, da sauran maki goma sha biyu.
Spieth ya ce Amurkawa na jin kamar suna da wani abu a hannunsu kuma suna da dalilin da zai sa su karfafa gwiwa, musamman ma Spieth da Justin Thomas wadanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma suna iya alfahari da cewa sun sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya nuna kansa mai tasiri sosai a wasan daga tee zuwa green kuma ya kafa misali.
Muryar murna ta ƙara ƙaruwa yayin da ya ci gaba da wasa. Wani muhimmin putt ya ba shi damar daidaitawa a cikin kashi na huɗu yayin da Thomas da shi suka jagoranci biyu a ƙasa bayan rami biyu.
Gwanin da ya yi a rami na 15 da ya sa suka ci wasan, ya jawo irin wannan kukan daga waɗanda suka ce ya yi imanin cewa 'yan wasan Amurka suna cikin wasan.
 Dole ne mutum ya kasance mai ƙuduri kuma ya mai da hankali kan wasan , in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage ga kowane daga cikin 'yan wasan, a yanzu.
An yi rami 18 don a nuna bambanci.
'Yan wasan da suka ci kwallo fiye da Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, kamar yadda tarihin Ryder Cup ya nuna.
Ƙungiyar 'yan wasan Turai ta lashe wasanni huɗu cikin huɗu kuma ba ta da damar yin kuskure.
Ba wai kawai Moliwood ne kawai ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun kuma tsere a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma a cikin ramuka tara na karshe a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan wasan, yadda suke nuna karfin su a tsakanin su da kuma yadda jama'a ke murna da su, ya nuna su a matsayin 'yan wasan da za a doke a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari farin ciki a kan yiwuwar samun nasara a Turai yayin da rana ke faɗuwa a filin wasan na Golf National.
Zai fi kyau a yi duka biyun a lokaci ɗaya a wuri dabam dabam.
Amma fa, ba a kai lokaci ba a yi maganar samun ɗaukaka a Turai.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun doke Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon safiya, yayin da yake wasa da Alex Noren.
Ƙara ƙwanƙwasa da kuma sau biyu a raga na farko ya jefa ɗan ƙasar Spain da kuma ɗan ƙasar Sweden cikin rami wanda ba za su iya fita ba.
Amma, a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimake ka.
Hudu da huɗu suna da ban sha'awa don a lura da su sosai saboda yadda ma'aurata suke hulɗa, da kuma irin shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun za su iya canzawa a cikin ƙwalƙashin ido.
Turai ta fi wasa a matsayin kungiya a yanzu kuma ta sami ci gaba mai yawa a ranar ƙarshe, amma wannan zaman na mutum huɗu ya kuma tabbatar da cewa Amurkawa suna da ƙarfin gwiwa don yin gwagwarmaya, wanda wasu suka yi shakkar hakan, musamman a cikin gida.
Ƙasar Turai ta ci 10-6 a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu damar cin nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta ci Amurka 10-6 a wasan kwallon kwando da kuma wasan tsere a ranar Asabar.
Ƙwararrun 'yan wasa biyu Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci wasan da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke cikin damuwa, wanda ya ba su damar samun maki hudu a yanzu.
Da yake sun ƙuduri aniyar riƙe kambun da suka yi hasara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, tawagar Thomas Bjorn ta Turai ta yi nasara da ci 3-1 a wasan kwallon kwando na safe a kan wata tawagar 'yan wasan Amurka da suka yi ta rikici.
Amurka ta nuna fice a wasan na hudu kuma ta lashe sau biyu, amma ba ta samu nasarar rufe gibin ba.
A ranar Lahadi, dole ne 'yan wasan Jim Furyk su ci maki takwas cikin 12 a wasan kwaikwayo na 'yan wasa guda biyu don su ci gaba da lashe gasar.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko a Turai da ta ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, waɗanda aka yi wa lakabi da  Molliwood  bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune kawai na biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka ci maki huɗu a wasanninsu huɗu na farko.
Bayan sun ci Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallo, sai suka ci Bryson Dechambeau, wanda shi ne ɗan Amirka, da kuma Woods da ya riga ya gaji da cin kwallo biyar da kuma huɗu.
Woods, wanda ya yi jinkiri a wasannin biyu na ranar Asabar, ya yi fice a wasu lokatai, amma yanzu ya yi hasarar wasanni 19 cikin 29 da ya buga a wasan kwallon kafa da kuma na gida da kuma na baya-bayan nan.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta don wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya haɗu da Henrik Stenson a wasan wasan, suka ci nasara 2-1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, lambobin duniya da na uku.
Ba a bar Turai ba a gasar da aka yi a kudu maso yammacin Paris, a cikin yanayi mai sanyi amma ba a yi ba.
'Yan wasan da suka ci nasara sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga 'yan wasan Amurka ta hanyar cin kwallo biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasarar da suka cancanci 2-1 a kan Jon Rahm na Spain da Ian Poulter a cikin kwallo hudu kuma sun sake doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a cikin kwallo huɗu, waɗanda suka rasa ramin farko da biyu.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, wata kungiya ta samu nasara ta maki hudu a wasan zakarun, duk da cewa kungiyar Furyk da ke rike da kambun ta yi wasa biyu ne kawai don ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Bayan sun kasance na biyu a kwanaki biyu, duk da haka, ba za su iya murmurewa daga harin da aka kai musu a ranar Lahadi ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za a iya yin watsi da makaman ba a kowane hali ba.
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da takunkumin ya karawa Koriya ta Arewa rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu ba a bar Koriya ta Arewa ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta a halin da ake ciki.
A taron shekara-shekara na hukumar, Ri Yong Ho ya ce Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki matakai masu muhimmanci a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwaje-gwajen nukiliya da makamin nukiliya, da rushe wuraren gwaje-gwajen nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ta dauka na hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
 Amma ba mu ga wata amsa daga Amurka ba , ya ce
Idan ba mu amince da Amurka ba, za mu ji tsoron tsaron ƙasarmu kuma a irin wannan yanayin ba za mu zama na farko da za mu yi watsi da makamai ba.
Yayin da yake maimaita sanannun zarge-zargen da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da adawar Washington ga tsarin da aka tsara na denuclearisation wanda a karkashinsa za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta dauki matakai a hankali, jawabin nasa ya kasance mai mahimmanci a cikin cewa ba ta ƙaryata game da ra'ayin na denuclearisation na unilateral kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana game da wata sanarwa ta Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump a ranar 12 ga Yuni a Singapore a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don yadda za a kawar da makamin nukiliya a yankin Koriya  yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi a kawo karshen yakin Koriya (1950-1953) a hukumance, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara watsar da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma ki amincewa da bukatar rage takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta nace kan Koriya ta Arewa ta fara yin nukiliya kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar sanya takunkumi don cimma burin ta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da adawa da "bayyanar karshen yaki".
 Wadanda suke tunanin cewa wannan hukunci zai iya sa mu kasa kasa ba su san mu ba.
Matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da sanya takunkumi yana kara mana rashin amincewa. 
Ri bai yi wani bayani ba game da taron na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump wanda shugaban Amurka ya gabatar a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon wannan makon.
Maimakon haka, Ministan ya yi nuni da tarurruka uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, kuma ya kara da cewa:  Idan da a ce Koriya ta Kudu ce ta ke da alhakin kawar da makaman nukiliya ba Amurka ba, da batun kawar da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba zai shiga irin wannan matsala ba. 
Duk da haka, sautin Ri a jawabinsa ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya bayyana a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba za a iya guje wa nukiliyoyin Koriya ta Arewa ba a kan yankin Amurka bayan da mummunan Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a kan manufa ta kashe kansa.
