Paul Barreira, Farfesa a fannin ilimin hauka a Harvard Medical School kuma babban darektan kula da kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta lura cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin barci sosai a cikin mako.
