Mako guda bayan jaridar gwamnatin kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu na talla a cikin wata jaridar Amurka, inda ta nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da Sin, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da jaridun Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da ƙarin da China Daily ta biya a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi yawan kasuwa a Iowa  bayan da ya zargi China da ƙoƙarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattawan Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Trump ya zargi Beijing da yin kutse a zaben Amurka, wanda jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na kamfen da Washington ke yi na matsawa China.
