 Bayan ganin irin wannan a irin wannan matashin shekaru  - ya shiga wasannin Olympics na farko yana dan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan shekaru uku - ya ce yana da wuya a samu wani wanda ya kai shekarunsa da ya fuskanci irin wannan yanayi na farin ciki da wahala.
