Za ku iya samun wannan bidiyon a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi a ƙarfe 11:15 na yamma.
Mickelson ya yi rashin lafiya a Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan da ya fi kowa tsalle a gasar Ryder Cup a yau Lahadi, amma dole ne ya sake farfadowa don kauce wa rashin nasara.
Mickelson, wanda ya halarci gasar shekara-shekara sau goma sha biyu, ya yi rikodin, ya yi watsi da kyaftin Jim Furyk na ranar Asabar da hudu da hudu.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya saba yi a Amurka, zakara mai sau biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin goyon baya da kuma gyara wasansa a filin wasa don magance ciwonsa.
