Kuma kamar dai wannan tseren ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson, a wasansa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya fuskanci Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar Open ta Birtaniya, wanda ya hada kai da Tommy Fleetwood a wannan makon don lashe wasanninsu hudu.
