Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ya rutsa da birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ba a samu bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da inda girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta faru.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga gidajensu sakamakon bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi na tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar ƙanƙara mai ƙanƙanta a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda aka kiyasta yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Garin na bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ya kai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
An kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin, wani yanki na gudanarwa wanda ke ƙasa da lardin, a 299 200 mazauna a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, amma ya fi yawa a Morowali, a gefen gabar Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami a lokuta da dama a cikin karni guda, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma yi tasiri a yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan iyakar Pacific kuma a kai a kai girgizar ƙasa tana girgiza ƙasar.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, babban girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gaɓar tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesia ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin waɗanda suka mutu sun kasance a Aceh.
