Girgizar kasa ta kashe mutane da dama a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da ta auku a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata.
Girgizar ƙasar da ta kai maki 7.5 ta jawo tsunami, kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
An yi rashin wutar lantarki da sadarwa kuma ana sa ran za a samu karin mutane da za su mutu a cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afku ne a tsakiyar Sulawesi, arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin Indonesia.
Bidiyo da ke yawo a shafukan sada zumunta na nuna yadda wannan ya shafi mutane.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya tashi a bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa a kan Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai hari a New York inda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yi ba a jihar don wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an ce ya yi amfani da wata babbar mota da ya yi hayar a Home Depot don ya kai hari a kan titin kekuna a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma wani mai hawan keke a watan Oktoba da ya gabata.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci a nuna cewa Saipov da gangan ya kashe mutane takwas da kuma yi wa mutane mummunan lahani, kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin takardar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin tuhumar za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar da kotu ta fitar.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa bisa tuhume-tuhume 22, ciki har da tuhumar kisa takwas bisa zargin karɓar kuɗi, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'o'in masu aikata laifi da kuma kisa ɗaya bisa laifin aikata laifi na lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci shiri mai zurfi da kuma shiri, in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kiran hanyar da Saipov ya yi amfani da ita ta "mummunan hali, mugunta da lalata".
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo rauni, lalacewa da asarar rayuka ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco , in ji sanarwar da aka yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Kudancin New York bai nemi hukuncin kisa ba a cikin shekaru goma na shari'a.
An samu wanda ake zargin Khalid Barnes da laifin kisan wasu 'yan kasuwa biyu na miyagun kwayoyi, amma daga baya aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumban 2009.
A karshe da aka yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a wata shari'a ta tarayya a New York a shekara ta 1953 a cikin shari'ar Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe saboda aikata laifuka na hada baki da leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a cikin shekaru biyu bayan yakin sanyi.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda asalinsa dan kasar Uzbekistan ne, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan wannan bala'i, a cewar bayanan kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu bincike cewa ya yi farin ciki da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an sa shi ya yi wannan harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon Daesh a wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya nemi a saka tutar Daesh a cikin ɗakinsa a asibiti.
Ya ce bai da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da ake yi masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare hakkin jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya bayyana cewa ya yi matukar bakin ciki game da shawarar da aka yanke na tuhumar Saipov.
"Muna ganin hukuncin da aka yanke na neman a yanke masa hukuncin kisa maimakon a amince da ikirarinsa na laifi a yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai iya ci gaba da ciwo da ke tattare da wadannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar lauyoyin Saipov ta riga ta gaya wa masu gabatar da kara kada su nemi a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
