A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan Turai sun yi tattaki a Birmingham kafin su shirya wani gangami na tsawon sa'o'i biyu a cikin gari.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi zanga-zanga da 'yan Conservative a kan Brexit bayan da suka kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
