Warren na da niyyar yin tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa 'yar majalisa ta Massachusetts ta tattauna game da makomar ta a ranar Asabar a wani taron jama'a a yammacin Massachusetts.
Warren, wanda ke yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, ya yi takarar sake tsayawa takara a watan Nuwamba, inda ya yi takara da Geoff Diehl, wakilin GOP a jihohin, wanda ya yi takarar shugabancin kamfen din Trump a Massachusetts a 2016.
Ta zama tauraruwar da ake hasashen za ta iya fafatawa da Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da rana a Holyoke shi ne karo na 36 da Trump ya gana da masu jefa kuri'a a wani taron jama'a tun lokacin da ya hau mulki.
Wani mai halarta ya tambaye ta ko tana da niyyar tsayawa takarar shugabancin.
Warren ya amsa da cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, wanda hakan ke nufin samun mace a matsayin shugaban kasa.
