Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a ragar Giants a Dundee
'Yan wasan Dundee Stars sun shawo kan rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite League ta ranar Juma'a a hannun Belfast Giants inda suka ci wasan dawowa da ci 5-3 a Dundee ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Giants sun ci kwallo biyu daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo daidaito a gida kafin Dwyer ya ba da damar zuwa Giants.
François Bouchard ya daidaita a Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallaye biyu, yana tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan shi ne kashi na uku na Elite League a wannan kakar don 'yan wasan Adam Keefe, wanda ya doke Dundee 2-1 a daren Juma'a a Belfast, bayan an kama shi.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da aka yi a kakar wasa ta bana tsakanin bangarorin biyu, bayan da Giants suka yi nasara a wasanni uku na karshe.
Dwyer ya ci gaba da wasa a minti na hudu, 3:35 na dare, ta hanyar bugun Kendall McFaull, yayin da David Rutherford ya ci Beauvillier wanda ya ninka minti huɗu bayan haka.
A lokacin wani lokaci mai cike da aiki, Sullivan ya dawo da gida a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya fara aiki a Cownie, a 15:16, tare da daidaituwa.
Dwyer ya jagoranci Giants kafin lokacin hutu na farko lokacin da ya zira kwallo na biyu na maraice a ƙarshen farkon lokaci.
Ƙungiyar 'yan wasan gida sun sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa tare da manufa ta hanyar lambar a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya jagoranci Dundee a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen rabi na biyu, don haka ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagarsa ta hanyar cin kwallaye na biyar a tsakiyar wasan.
Giants, wadanda yanzu sun yi rashin nasara hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka gabata, za su kara da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
