A cikin yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, an fara da rikici, kuma duk da cewa har yanzu ba a gama ba, amma a cikin dogon lokaci, rashin jituwa tsakanin kasashen biyu zai iya amfanar da Beijing, a cewar masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da gargaɗin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da China ke fitarwa, da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, da karafa da kuma aluminum.
Babban tashin ya zo ne a wannan makon tare da sabbin haraji kan kayayyaki da suka kai dalar Amurka biliyan 200 (£150 biliyan), wanda ya shafi rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Kowane lokaci, Beijing ta mayar da martani ta hanyar, kwanan nan ta sanya haraji na kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin yin kama da Amurka, kuma ba ta da tsammanin cewa tattalin arzikinta na biyu a duniya zai yi kasa a gwiwa nan ba da daɗewa ba.
Komawa baya ga Washington yana nufin yin biyayya ga buƙatun, amma yin biyayya a fili ga Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma masana sun yi amannar cewa idan Beijing ta taka rawar da ya dace, to matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya yin tasiri a kan kasar Sin a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin kasashen biyu.
 Gaskiyar cewa wani gaggawar yanke shawara a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da koma bayan tattalin arziki a kowanne daga cikin kasashen, ya fi hatsari fiye da yadda masu sa ido suka yarda a baya , Abigail Grace, wata abokiyar bincike da ke mayar da hankali kan Asiya, ta shaida wa kungiyar tunani ta Cibiyar Sabon Tsaron Amurka.
Syria ta  shiryuwa  don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta maraba da 'yan gudun hijirar da suka dawo kuma ta nemi taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace bayan shekaru bakwai na yaki.
Yayin da yake jawabi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje, Walid al-Moualem, ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar yana samun ci gaba.
 A yau, yanayin da ake ciki ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro sakamakon ci gaba da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci , in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyaran wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da yanayin da ya saba.
Yanzu dai an samu dama ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijira cikin yardar rai zuwa kasar da aka tilasta musu barin ta saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki da aka dauka a bangaren daya da ke damun rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun bayan da aka fara yakin basasa a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke da bukatar taimako a ƙasar har yanzu suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta maraba da taimakon da za a bayar don sake gina wannan kasa da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka bayar ba, ko kuma na wasu kasashe da ke tallafa wa 'yan tawayen ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder a Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta hanyar doke Team Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe na 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu dai Amurka ta sha kashi a gasar Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun daga shekarar 1993.
Ƙasar Turai ta sake lashe gasar a lokacin da tawagar kyaftin Thomas Bjorn ta Denmark ta ƙaru da maki 14.5 da ake bukata don doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya buga kwallo a rami na 16 a rami na 3, ya ba da wasan da ya yi a Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a dukkan wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka kai 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi 5-4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kowa a Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne ɗan wasan golf mafi ƙanƙanta a duniya, ya yi nasara da Ian Poulter ɗan Ingila, wanda ƙila shi ne ɗan wasan da ya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta ƙarshe.
Tsohon ɗan wasan gasar Ryder Cup takwas, ɗan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama zakaran zakarun Turai na kowane lokaci tare da jimlar maki 25.5 a rayuwarsa.
