A cikin rahoton da Hukumar Kiwon Daji da Kifi ta Florida ta fitar kwanan nan, an nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan ruwan sama a wasu wurare a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar CPF, ana samun rahotanni game da yanayin furewa da ba daidai ba a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - wanda ke haifar da fargabar raguwar maida hankali.
Ruwa mai ruwan sama ya rufe kusan kilomita 209 (130 miles) na bakin teku, daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kuducin Lee Counties.
Ana samun wasu tsibiran a nisan kilomita 10 daga Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kaɗan ne fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan sama a yankin Pasco.
An ba da rahoton ƙananan taro a cikin ko kuma daga cikin yankin Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin Hillsborough County, mafi girma a cikin Manatee County, mafi girma a cikin ƙasa a cikin Sarasota County ko kuma daga cikin teku, matsakaicin taro a cikin Charlotte County da ƙananan taro a cikin Lee County da kuma daga cikin wannan, manyan taro a cikin ƙasa ko kuma daga cikin Collier County.
Ana samun har yanzu cututtukan na numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton cutar huhu a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
